json.text: This is Banshee, stealthy and ranged.
Using the deceiving power of sound, she can infiltrate nearly any situation.
While not built to take damage, Banshee deals it out in spades.
Sonic Boom can incapacitate or kill enemies in front of her with an
armor piercing shockwave that pushes them away.
Reminiscent of ancient earth technology, sonar reveals enemies to Banshee’s entire team,
revealing their weak spots and location.
Silence allows Banshee to limit her enemies perception and response times
causing attacks to go unnoticed by those affected.
Cover your ears, Tenno. When Sound Quake is used, Banshee releases ultrasonic waves
to take out any enemies who dare enter its range.
Banshee can be upgraded to enhance her effectiveness at longer range.
For limited close combat situations, all of Banshee’s core abilities will benefit from utilizing
increased range mods. Using an increased strength mod will positively affect
Sonic Boom and Sound Quake’s destructive power.
Installing increased duration mods will benefit Sonar and Silence,
allowing Banshee to take more time formulating her attack plan.
No one puts Banshee in a corner, Tenno. The element of surprise is in her favor.
